  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, my professional name is Aniko Veres-Fe, which Aniko Veres is my maiden name and Fe was added because of other things.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is the January 16, 1995 edition of magazine, which was an Auschwitz memorial edition that I happened open by chance.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I found myself in this picture, which represents us, part of the 1,000 Hungarian girls, on our way from Auschwitz to this German factory.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I happen to be the tall girl right on the crease.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is a homemade photograph of the-- of a maquette-- of the only holocaust memorial that I ever designed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I always believe just like I don't think that-- that words can convey-- convey the inexplicable, the-- the-- the human tragedy that was the Holocaust, I feel the same way about the ability of visual arts to do that.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this I see as preferably a larger than life size bronze-- what--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--would call it?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's thin slab, like a--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--slab, where the figures, the figure of a family, would be cut out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it's of the void, the void that it represents in the lives, in the hearts of the survivors as well.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is a side view, obviously.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the other part of the sculpture is that it would have to be on a large bare terrain.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the way the sun moves or reflectors, it always casts a shadow where the figures emerge in light.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I feel simplicity is the strongest.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's the only thing that I would hope to one day to execute.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
